description:
On this edition of Parazeit Jack and Miles discuss Rage going back on a 40-stop tour, Valentine's Day is coming up, Cindy Crawford's son gets a face tattoo, a new fossil discovered in Canada, the New Hampshire Primary is tomorrow, and Bill Gates DID NOT buy a Hydrogen yacht.
